          prosecute anyone who does. The Extinction Symbol was designed in 2011 by street artist ESP, who loans XR
          usage on the same basis: www.extinctionsymbol.info.</p>
        <p><%= link_to('LOGIN', new_user_session_path) %> &nbsp; <%= link_to('LOGOUT', destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete) %></p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-2 mx-auto">
        <h5 class="font-weight-bold text-center mt-3 mb-4">DONATE</h5>
        <ul class="list-unstyled list-inline text-center py-2">
          <li class="list-inline-item">
            <a href="https://chuffed.org/pay/campaign/62932" target="_blank" type="button" class="btn btn-outline-success">Donate</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-2 mx-auto">
        <h5 class="font-weight-bold text-center mt-3 mb-4">NEWSLETTER</h5>
        <ul class="list-unstyled list-inline text-center py-2">
          <li class="list-inline-item">
            <a href="https://actionnetwork.org/forms/newsletter-sign-up-17?source=direct_link&" target="_blank" type="button" class="btn btn-outline-success">Sign
              up</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row d-flex align-items-center">
      <div class="col-md-7 col-lg-8">
        <p class="text-center text-md-left">Â© 2020 Copyright: Extinction Rebellion</p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-5 col-lg-4 ml-lg-0">
        <div class="text-center text-md-right">
          <ul class="list-unstyled list-inline">
            <li class="list-inline-item">
              <a href="https://www.facebook.com/ExtinctionRebellion/" target="_blank" class="btn-floating btn-sm rgba-white-slight mx-1">
                <i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i>
              </a>
            </li>
            <li class="list-inline-item">
              <a href="https://twitter.com/ExtinctionR" target="_blank" class="btn-floating btn-sm rgba-white-slight mx-1">
                <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>
              </a>
            </li>
            <li class="list-inline-item">
              <a href="https://www.instagram.com/extinctionrebellion/" target="_blank" class="btn-floating btn-sm rgba-white-slight mx-1">
                <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
              </a>
            </li>
            <li class="list-inline-item">
              <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYThdLKE6TDwBJh-qDC6ICA" target="_blank" class="btn-floating btn-sm rgba-white-slight mx-1">
                <i class="fab fa-youtube"></i>
              </a>
            </li>
            <li class="list-inline-item">
              <a href="http://fetchrss.com/rss/5ec6a57f8a93f8ff678b45685ec6a56f8a93f8d5668b4567.xml" target="_blank" class="btn-floating btn-sm rgba-white-slight mx-1">
                <i class="fas fa-rss"></i>
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
<!--Footer End-->

<a id="back-to-top" href="#" class="btn btn-light btn-lg back-to-top" role="button"><i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i></a>

</body>
</html>